      <pubDate>Mon, 05 Jan 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/i/wannsee-blackout/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Since yesterday, several lines have not been operating due to someone’s “vandalism” in Berlin.&#xA;I found there was a power outage at Wannsee station, and it was completely dark inside the station.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;I took the RE1 to Wannsee and then used a bus to get to work.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Here is a beautiful snowy view of the bus stop at Wannsee station. This was the only thing that made me feel good in the situation.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
